title: President Donald J. Trump Is Paving The Way For Energy Infrastructure Development – The White House
content:
Fact Sheets			

		Energy & Environment	

Issued on:
April 10, 2019
When it comes to the future of America’s energy needs, we will find it, we will dream it, and we will build it.
						President Donald J. Trump					DEVELOPING ENERGY INFRASTRUCTURE: President Trump is signing two Executive Orders to streamline Federal processes surrounding energy infrastructure development.UNLEASHING AMERICAN ENERGY: President Trump is promoting an efficient domestic energy market that creates jobs and provides affordable, reliable energy to consumers.ACHIEVING ENERGY DOMINANCE: President Trump is committed to responsibly developing our Nation’s abundant resources and advancing American energy dominance.
